  <thing id="ipS2DurEye" name="Sarenrae&apos;s Baleful Eye" description="As long as you carry {i}Durindana{/i} before you, your channel energy gains a +2 bonus on the DC and a bonus to damage vs undead equal to your caster level. These affects only apply when you are using your channel energy to damage undead." compset="Ability" summary="Channel Energy vs Undead DC +2 and your Caster Level as bonus damage.">
