  <thing id="iS2Lightni" name="Lightning Sword" description="The {i}lightning sword{/i} is a {i}+2 shocking burst mithral short sword{/i}. Used by the Wind Duke Icosiol on the battlefield of Pesh, the {i}lightning sword{/i} is the companion blade to the {i}sword of Aaqa{/i}. The {i}lightning sword&apos;s{/i} pommel is a single huge star sapphire that glitters with electrical energy.\n\nThree times per day by drawing the {i}lightning sword{/i}, the wielder can gain the effects of a {i}fly{/i} spell (caster level 9). This effect springs into being as part of the act of drawing the sword.\n\nIf the wielder fights with the {i}lightning sword{/i} and the {i}sword of Aaqa{/i}, he may strike the two swords together as a standard action to generate 30-foot line of sonic energy. All creatures in this area take 6d6 sonic damage (Reflex DC 18 half ). This ability can be used three times per day." compset="MagicWep" summary="The {i}lightning sword{/i} is a {i}+2 shocking burst mithral temple sword{/i}." uniqueness="useronce">
